### Summary

**Total Estimated Effort:** ~3,050 lines (code + tests + docs)

**Deliverables:**
- ✅ Gmail OAuth authentication (~650 lines)
- ✅ Google Drive sync engine (~850 lines)
- ✅ Email to markdown converter (~500 lines)
